      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12">
          <h1 class="visiontext">MY VISION FOR <span id="animatedTextTwo">BURLINGTON</span></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12">
          <p class="visionsubtext">My vision for Burlington is one where all people feel safe and welcome, where we live, work and play together as good neighbors collaborating and being community for each other.
            I see a Burlington where community leaders are engaged with community members and hear concerns in a way to invite community input to meet the challenges we face.</p>
          <p class="visionsubtext">I see a Burlington where all are able to find the resources they need to live and thrive–livable wage jobs, affordable housing, safe and livable communities.
            I see a Burlington that embraces our diversity and maximizes the best of who we are.
            I see a Burlington that embraces community, collaboration and compassion for all.</p>
          <h3 style="color: #fffcf5; font-weight: bold;">Leadership Matters</h3>
          <p class="visionsubtext">This vision of Burlington cannot be achieved with 15-minute council meetings and leaders who show up in the community once or twice a year.
            This vision of Burlington can be achieved with a leader that shows up, a leader that listens, a leader that works hard for every citizen and calls on our council to work hard as well.</p>
          <h3 style="color: #fffcf5; font-weight: bold;">Vote Beth Kennett for Burlington Mayor</h3>
          <p class="visionsubtext">I will work every day to be that leader who will help us join together to build a safe, welcoming, livable community for all.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
